%noscript
  .alert.alert-danger
    Please activate JavaScript.

- flash.each do |key, value|
  .alert.alert-dismissible{class: "alert-#{bootstrap_color key}", role: "alert"}
    %button.close{type: "button", "data-dismiss" => "alert"}
      %span{"aria-hidden" => "true"} &times;
      %span.sr-only Close
    = value